precis:
Enactment of DESIGNATED PROVISIONS (CUSTOMS) REGULATIONS which designate
selected provisions of the Customs Act, the Customs Tariff and a number of
Regulations made thereunder as contraventions the breach of which may lead
to the imposition of an administrative monetary penalty of up to $25,000.
